China to Regulate Banks’ Wealth Management Product Sales: Cbrc

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-10-09T10:20:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-09/china-to-regulate-banks-wealth-management-product-sales-cbrc.html
China issued rules to regulate sales
of wealth management products by commercial banks, the China
Banking Regulatory Commission said on its website.  Banks are not allowed to use sales or purchases of wealth
management products to manipulate “regulatory indicators,”
according to the rules, which will take effect from 2012.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bloomberg News in Beijing at 
